FBIS3-31600 "dreeu035_d_94015" FBIS-EEU-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 SLOVAKIA World Bank Grants $80 Million Loan LD1902120894 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1100 GMT 19 Feb 94 LD1902120894 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1100 GMT 19 Feb 94 Language: Slovak Article Type:BFN [Text] An agreement on an $80-million loan to the Slovak Republic has been signed at the World Bank in Washington. The loan is earmarked for economic recovery and will be used to boost foreign currency reserves. The terms of the loan are advantageous, and its repayment will begin in August 1999.
